CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772197440
OL,3,CLocal businesses are "feeling the
OL,4,Cpinch" as major town centre roadworks
OL,5,Ccontinue
OL,7,FThe multi-million-pound Farnham
OL,8,FInfrastructure Programme, led by
OL,9,FSurrey County Council, began in
OL,10,FFebruary 2025. While the project aims
OL,11,Fto revitalise the area with wider
OL,12,Fpavements and new seating, local
OL,13,Fbusinesses say the ongoing noise, road
OL,14,Fclosures, and traffic queues are
OL,15,Fdriving shoppers away.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772197440
OL,3,CLocal businesses are "feeling the
OL,4,Cpinch" as major town centre roadworks
OL,5,Ccontinue
OL,7,FFor many who usually visit the town
OL,8,Ffor leisure, the roadworks have turned
OL,9,Fa quick trip into a challenge. Steve
OL,10,FHamilton, who runs Hamilton's Tea
OL,11,FHouse, says the impact on footfall is
OL,12,Fnoticeable.
OL,14,F"What we've noticed is people are
OL,15,Fdeciding not to come in just as a
OL,16,Flittle bit of a leisure tour," he
OL,17,Fsaid. "It's now a bit of a trek...
OL,18,Fpeople are only coming in if they
OL,19,Freally have to, or maybe once a month
OL,20,Finstead of once every week".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772197440
OL,3,CLocal businesses are "feeling the
OL,4,Cpinch" as major town centre roadworks
OL,5,Ccontinue
OL,7,FOther business owners, like Jenny
OL,8,FYoung from Wild Thyme, admit that
OL,9,Fwhile the work should eventually
OL,10,Fimprove the flow of traffic, many
OL,11,Fshops are currently "feeling the
OL,12,Fpinch".
OL,14,FThe project is designed to make the
OL,15,Ftown centre more resilient and
OL,16,Fpedestrian-friendly. Key improvements
OL,17,Finclude:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772197440
OL,3,CLocal businesses are "feeling the
OL,4,Cpinch" as major town centre roadworks
OL,5,Ccontinue
OL,7,FDespite the long-term benefits,
OL,8,Fresidents told ITV Meridian they are
OL,9,Fcurrently avoiding the area. One
OL,10,Fshopper said: "It's very difficult at
OL,11,Fthe moment as nothing is really
OL,12,Fmoving... sadly, a lot of people try
OL,13,Fto avoid Farnham".
OL,15,FThere have been growing calls for
OL,16,Fparking charges to be axed or
OL,17,Fsignificantly reduced to entice
OL,18,Fshoppers back into the town.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772197440
OL,3,CLocal businesses are "feeling the
OL,4,Cpinch" as major town centre roadworks
OL,5,Ccontinue
OL,7,FWaverley Borough Council previously
OL,8,Ftrialled a "#1 after 1pm" scheme over
OL,9,Fthe Christmas period, but they have
OL,10,Fresisted calls for entirely free
OL,11,Fparking.
OL,13,FCouncillor Tony Fairclough, from
OL,14,FWaverley Borough Council, said: "Where
OL,15,Ffree parking was previously offered,
OL,16,Fit led to spaces being taken by
OL,17,Fcommuters rather than shoppers, so it
OL,18,Ffailed to provide a boost for local
OL,19,Ftraders."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772197440
OL,3,CLocal businesses are "feeling the
OL,4,Cpinch" as major town centre roadworks
OL,5,Ccontinue
OL,7,FInstead, the council is proposing to
OL,8,Ffreeze the cost of stays between two
OL,9,Fand eight hours to encourage visitors
OL,10,Fto stay longer. They are also
OL,11,Fconsidering a "Farnham Will Be Open
OL,12,FFor Business Again" celebration once
OL,13,Fthe current phase of work is completed
OL,14,Fthis Easter.
OL,16,FSurrey County Council insists the
OL,17,Fworks remain on schedule for
OL,18,Fcompletion later this year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
